Package com.msasc.lib.db

Class FieldList

java.lang.Object
com.msasc.lib.db.FieldList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Field>
public class FieldList extends Object implements Iterable<Field>
An ordered list of fields that can efficiently be accessed by index or by key or field alias.
Author:
Miquel Sas
